The requirements are currently the following:
numpy >= 1.7.0
scipy >= 0.13.0
jcc >= 2.17

This requirements will be installed automatically, if you use a python package
manager like pip or easy_install.

For the stallone wrapper you need a JDK to compile the wrapper code. So far, we
recommend at least JDK 1.6

To install this package to your home directory, please call:

easy_install --user .

If you want to update the stallone wrapper module for some reason (updated the
library jars), please call:

# pwd is emma2 project root
REBUILD_STALLONE=y easy_install --user .
